{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle friends and family in an epic, high-stakes game of musical chairs !<br>Throw yourself into the fight with your strength or outwit your opponents by sneaking in at just the right moment to claim victory and become the ultimate International Musical Chairs Champion! Perfect for party nights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414020/extras/Gameplay.gif?t=1740392008\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blast away your opponents with a powerful shout or hurl objects across the arena to knock them off course! Send them splashing into the water to keep them from victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414020/extras/Features.gif?t=1740392008\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Snag power-ups to give you the advantage, crazy sponsors of this unique sporting universe will parachute in game-changing power-ups\u2014grab them to gain the upper hand!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play within unique arenas, each packed with unexpected twists and challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414020/extras/ar\u00e8nes.gif?t=1740392008\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your contender based on your preferred musical tastes, (rock, folk, jazz, classical and more) and bask in the crowd's roar on your way to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414020/extras/perso_controles.gif?t=1740392008\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai